- [ ] ExecutionRequest includes toolchain field
- [ ] Daemon API parses toolchain from requests
- [ ] Transfer pipeline wraps commands with rustup run
- [ ] Hook detects and passes toolchain through pipeline
- [ ] Serialization/deserialization works correctly
- [ ] Tests cover protocol changes

